 all smiles on this occasion, competitors acknowledged that's not always the case when they are rushed off their feet at work.\", \"from\": 3400, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this occasion\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"competitors\", \"from\": 3438, \"to\": 3449}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3489}, {\"ngram\": \"their feet\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"work\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The customer may always be right in other countries, but the waiter or waitress has the final word in France, feeding their reputation for being abrupt, moody, and even rude at times.\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3637, \"end\": 3643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999998969222892, \"rank\": 5.676301951374686e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The customer\", \"from\": 3535, \"to\": 3547}, {\"ngram\": \"other countries\", \"from\": 3571, \"to\": 3586}, {\"ngram\": \"the waiter\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3602}, {\"ngram\": \"waitress\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"the final word\", \"from\": 3619, \"to\": 3633}, {\"ngram\": \"their reputation\", \"from\": 3653, \"to\": 3669}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 3712, \"to\": 3717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"French pride means that in little professions like this, they do not want to be trampled on,\\\" said Thierry Petit, 60, who is retiring in April after 40 years of waiting tables.\", \"from\": 3720, \"to\": 3897, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3721, \"end\": 3727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.5722790116153009, \"rank\": 0.74615484571911, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 3820, \"end\": 3827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Thierry\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Augustin_Thierry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"little professions\", \"from\": 3748, \"to\": 3766}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3863}, {\"ngram\": \"40 years\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3878}, {\"ngram\": \"waiting tables\", \"from\": 3882, \"to\": 3896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's not lack of respect, rather it's more a state of mind,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 3909, \"to\": 3913}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 3917, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"a state\", \"from\": 3943, \"to\": 3950}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Switching to English, he added: \\\"It's very Frenchie\\\".\", \"from\": 3970, \"to\": 4023, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4013, \"end\": 4021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenchie_(film)\", \"score\": 0.6885437919961173, \"rank\": 0.3906249999998979, \"text\": \"Frenchie\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenchie_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenchie_(film)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"English\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 3990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The capital's Mayor, Anne Hidalgo, said cafes and restaurants are \\\"really the soul of Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4046, \"end\": 4058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anne Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anne_Hidalgo\"}, {\"begin\": 4111, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.183375841503011e-19, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The capital's Mayor\", \"from\": 4025, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"cafes\", \"from\": 4065, \"to\": 4070}, {\"ngram\": \"restaurants\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4086}, {\"ngram\": \"the soul\", \"from\": 4099, \"to\": 4107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The bistrot is where we go to meet people, where we go for our little coffee, our little drink, where we also go to argue, to love and embrace each other,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 4120, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bistrot\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4132}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4156, \"to\": 4162}, {\"ngram\": \"our little coffee\", \"from\": 4180, \"to\": 4197}, {\"ngram\": \"our little drink\", \"from\": 4199, \"to\": 4215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The caf\\u00e9 and the bistrot are life.\\\"\", \"from\": 4288, \"to\": 4324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The caf\\u00e9\", \"from\": 4289, \"to\": 4297}, {\"ngram\": \"the bistrot\", \"from\": 4302, \"to\": 4313}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 4318, \"to\": 4322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"- Associated Press with additional reporting Doing it tough on a luxury 15-day river cruise.\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"- Associated Press\", \"from\": 4326, \"to\": 4344}, {\"ngram\": \"additional reporting\", \"from\": 4350, \"to\": 4370}, {\"ngram\": \"a luxury 15-day river cruise\", \"from\": 4389, \"to\": 4417}]}]}"